text.section:
A member's membership automatically terminates:
When any member of the Commission appointed from among judges in the State ceases to be a judge;
When any member appointed from among those admitted to practice law becomes a judge;
When any member representing the public becomes a judge or is admitted to the practice of law in this State or has a financial relationship with or receives compensation from a judge or a person admitted to practice law in this State; or
When any member ceases to be a resident of the State.
